Subject: drm/amd/display: Train DPIA links with fallback
Git-commit: edfb2693471f593856df915cd24c1b62ffaf978c
Patch-mainline: v5.16-rc1
References: jsc#PED-1166 jsc#PED-1168 jsc#PED-1170 jsc#PED-1218 jsc#PED-1220 jsc#PED-1222 jsc#PED-1223 jsc#PED-1225

[Why & How]
Conventional links are trained with fallback during sink detection.
Have DPIA links trained with fallback too.

